1
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:51,760
Yanwang.

2
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:53,840
Yanwang.

3
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:55,280
Yanwang.

4
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:57,320
CAT: Yanwang.

5
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:57,850
Yanwang.

6
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,320
Liu Ma, stop right there.

7
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,200
Don't run.

8
00:01:11,039 --> 00:01:12,360
Pay up.

9
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,160
The outsider Anan brought back

10
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,290
hasn't woken up yet?

11
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,800
Get ready. The ritual needs a live sacrifice.

12
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,200
I'll bring him over soon.

13
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,360
Take me there.

14
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,040
We need a live sacrifice.

15
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,920
Why is this guy leaving through the window?

16
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,440
Good luck.

17
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,760
Catch that young man.

18
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,680
Catch him.

19
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,460
My instrument.

20
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:24,120
So you don't mean me, the living one.

21
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,640
It's a society ruled by law. Even it didn't die.

22
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,360
How could I kill you?

23
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,800
Sit down.

24
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,640
Let's get to know each other.

25
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,200
I'm Anan.

26
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,720
I'm your fan, Mr. Liu Ma.

27
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,460
You have the wrong person.

28
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,040
I get it.

29
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,159
Big shots keep a low profile.

30
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,280
But I recognized you right away.

31
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,820
Where is my bag?

32
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,880
Thanks.

33
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:11,500
Mr. Liu Ma, where are you staying?

34
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:15,180
Are there any hotels or guesthouses nearby?

35
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,320
You can stay at my place.

36
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,600
We have everything there.

37
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,930
Stay as long as you like.

38
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,290
I don't want to impose. Thanks.

39
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,040
Teacher Liu Ma.

40
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,580
Teacher Liu Ma.

41
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,440
Looking for inspiration? Are you alone?

42
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,480
Do you want a free guide who knows

43
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,010
everything about Lincang?

44
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,280
I'm looking for Yanwang.

45
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,320
Looking for the King of Hell?

46
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,480
It's raining now.

47
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,159
It's pitch black out there.

48
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,080
I'm worried about you being alone.

49
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,000
Do I know you?

50
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,680
We're friends. It's different.

51
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:52,040
We just met. We're not friends.

52
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,100
Stop following me.

53
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,080
Then let's add each other on WeChat.

54
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,010
My phone is dead.

55
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,800
My family runs a restaurant. I know a lot of people.

56
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,600
In the nearby villages and towns,

57
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,680
there's almost no one I don't know.

58
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,320
I can definitely help find him.

59
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:03,880
Anan.

60
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,440
Back to work.

61
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,320
Coming.

62
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,280
Take this.

63
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,720
Well,

64
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,880
contact me if you need anything.

65
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,600
Freeze!

66
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,159
Police!

67
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,480
I really got lost.

68
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,940
I didn't steal any tea.

69
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,200
Villagers reported that

70
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:02,920
someone's stealing tea from the ancient trees.

71
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,840
We've been on a stakeout for days.

72
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,840
Look at you.

73
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,920
Why aren't you asleep in the middle of the night?

74
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,840
What are you doing wandering around the tea mountain?

75
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,720
Start talking.

76
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,650
I came from out of town to find someone.

77
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,160
I booked a guesthouse,

78
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,040
but the GPS took me the wrong way,

79
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,960
so I got lost.

80
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,040
Nine out of ten people we catch

81
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,000
say the exact same thing.

82
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:23,560
You're looking for someone but don't even have ID.

83
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,560
Stop pretending.

84
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,040
I do have ID.

85
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,730
It's right in my wallet.

86
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:28,720
Wallet?

87
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,280
Where?

88
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,930
There's no wallet here.

89
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,280
We'll verify your identity.

90
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,920
We need to look into the situation further.

91
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,159
If you're really innocent,

92
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,760
we'll definitely let you go.

93
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:48,640
How about this.

94
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,560
What's the number for your family or friends?

95
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,820
Call them to come over.

96
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,000
I came to Lincang alone.

97
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,060
I don't have any friends here either.

98
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,250
- Mr. Liu Ma.
- Mr. Liu Ma.

99
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,800
- I knew you would call me.
- I knew you would call me.
